  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of Oxazolidinone to Treat Pneumonia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2, Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Blind Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of RX-1741 in the Treatment of Adult Patients With Mild to Moderate Severity of Community-Acquired Pneumonia (CAP)</official_title>
